We must ever preach the gospel,
Thus our friends and neighbors gain;
House to house with vital partners,
That our new ones will remain.
We must ever preach the gospel,
Loving them as our dear children,
We must ever preach the gospel
Through the word and prayer and singing,
We must ever preach the gospel,
For the building of the Body,
